ent epidemic\nthresholds, with the branching process approximation being more in agreement\nwith simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Dec 2015 17:17:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2016 14:34:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2016 17:43:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-15"}
