ate superconductors, and\ninterpret the properties of the pseudogap regime in the framework of the FL*\ntheory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Dec 2015 21:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Dec 2015 19:55:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-26"}
