ces in the inferred mass build-up\nof galactic halos and we suggest that care must be taken to ensure a physically\nmeaningful match between the galaxy-formation physics of semi-analytic models\nand the halo finders supplying their input.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 03:28:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Mar 2016 01:11:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-20"}
