e for the igBPs\nto look smaller and weaker, diffuse faster, move faster and further in a\nstraighter path.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 15:39:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
